id: pm-um4g
title: "GH-586: graph audit severity and code summaries mix finding and affected-item units"
description: "GitHub issue #586 reports that pm graph audit findings_by_severity counts findings while findings_by_code sums affected items, making one response envelope internally ambiguous for agents and analytics."
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 2
tags[3]: agent-ux,github,graph
created_at: "2026-07-18T07:14:14.088Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-18T11:37:36.056Z"
assignee: maintainer-agent
author: codex-sdk-vcs-20260718
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: Audit summary fields use explicitly named consistent units or expose both finding_count and affected_item_count with contract docs and regression coverage.
parent: pm-6x7o
risk: low
confidence: high
