comments[4]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-18T07:14:14.088Z",codex-sdk-vcs-20260718,"Duplicate check 2026-07-18: exact all-status title search returned zero; AND search across graph audit severity/count terms found no canonical issue. Created from https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/586 and linked to active graph primitives pm-ju83 plus governance parent pm-6x7o; left open and unclaimed because this PR does not implement it."
  "2026-07-18T10:52:19.107Z",maintainer-agent,"Implementation evidence: reproduced the reported behavior on the current build; implemented the shared SDK/CLI contract wave; focused build and regression suite pass. Repo-wide gates and isolated package proof are next."
  "2026-07-18T11:33:20.112Z",maintainer-agent,"Verification evidence: isolated packed-package graph audit reported finding_count=1 and affected_subjects_by_severity.error=2 for a two-item ordering cycle, preserving homogeneous aggregation units."
  "2026-07-18T11:37:31.459Z",maintainer-agent,"Gate evidence: pnpm test:coverage passed 310 files/5906 tests at 100% statements (38887), branches (27366), functions (7917), and lines (37864). pnpm lint, typecheck, contracts:check, docs link gate, secret scan, git diff --check, and the item-linked sandbox test all passed."
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-18T11:37:36.056Z",maintainer-agent,"Graph summary keys must use homogeneous units: findings_by_* counts finding rows, while affected_subjects_by_* counts represented graph subjects."
